### Лаба 2 — порядок: Admin login → Create → Client login → Activate → Check
@baseUrl = https://localhost:8443
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}
@clientToken = {{loginClient.response.body.accessToken}}

### 1. Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin1234!"
}

### 2. Создать лицензию (только ADMIN), владелец client (id=2)
# @name createLicense
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/license
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "typeId": 1,
  "ownerId": 2,
  "deviceCount": 3,
  "description": "Демо"
}

### 3. Client (владелец)
# @name loginClient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "client",
  "password": "Client1234!"
}

### 4. Активация — только владелец (подставь code из createLicense)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/license/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "activationKey": "КОД_ИЗ_CREATE",
  "deviceMac": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF",
  "deviceName": "PC-1"
}

### 5. Проверка (не меняет БД, только TicketResponse)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/license/check
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceMac": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
}

### 6. Продление — снова Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/license/renew
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "КОД_ИЗ_CREATE"
}
